desc: Woof-It Healthy Dog Treats are hand-made and oven baked right here in Melbourne Australia. At Woof-It our passion is to provide a safe healthy vegetable snack. Our treats are made with vegetables, Xylitol free peanut butter, Rice Flour, milled oats and flaxseeds with our hero ingredient Organic Canine flaxseed Oil.

layout.text: Woof-It is PASSIONATE about rewarding dogs with love and longevity by adding a healthy SAFE snack of VEGETABLES to their diet.
